signatures.text: inline fun <K> CharSequence.associateBy( keySelector: (Char) -> K): Map<K, Char>
signatures.desc: Returns a Map containing the characters from the given char sequence indexed by the key returned from keySelector function applied to each character.

signatures.text: inline fun <K, V> CharSequence.associateBy( keySelector: (Char) -> K, valueTransform: (Char) -> V): Map<K, V>
signatures.desc: Returns a Map containing the values provided by valueTransform and indexed by keySelector functions applied to characters of the given char sequence.
